      "content": "i just feel like my being here is a constant drain on them. every cent i spend, every bit of stress i bring home... it's like i'm just robbing them of a better life. if i wasn't even in the picture, they could actually breathe and just be happy without worrying about me. it's like the most selfless thing i could even think of is just... not being a burden anymore.",
